Casualty is an emergency medical drama, broadcast on BBC One in the UK. This is a list of characters of Casualty, both present and past.

Notes[edit]

Appearances
  1. ^ Cathy Shipton originally departed the series on 11 December 1993, before returning on 21 February 1998 and departing on 12 April 2003. She has since appeared on 23 and 24 September 2006, 29 and 30 August 2015 and 25 June 2016 for guest appearances, before returning permanently in August 2016.
  2. ^ Amanda Mealing guest starred in three episodes between 2004 and 2007 prior to joining the main cast on 29 March 2014.
  3. ^ William Beck originally departed the series on 15 December 2012, before returning on 25 October 2014.
  4. ^ Azuka Oforka originally appeared in the series on 1 October 2011, before returning on 18 August 2012.
  5. ^ Michael Stevenson originally appeared in the series on 28 April 2012, before returning on 31 August 2013 and departing on 22 March 2014. He returned again on 11 October 2014.
  6. ^ Chelsea Halfpenny originally departed the series on 14 November 2015, and returned on 30 July 2016.
  7. ^ Jenny Howe appears in both Casualty and Holby City on a recurring basis as Lexy Morrell.
  8. ^ Rebecca Ryan originally departed the series on 29 April 2017, and returned on 17 February 2018.
  9. ^ Brenda Fricker appeared in the role as a regular from 1986 to 1990, returned for two one-off appearances in 1998 and 2007, before returning for four episodes in August 2010.
  10. ^ Alex Walkinshaw originally departed the series on 29 June 2014, and guest appeared on 27 August 2016.
  11. ^ Sam Grey originally departed the series on 1 May 2010, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  12. ^ Martina Laird originally departed the series on 18 November 2006, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  13. ^ Ben Turner originally departed the series on 10 December 2011, and will guest appear on 27 August 2016.
  14. ^ James Redmond originally departed the series on 18 October 2008, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  15. ^ Steven Miller originally departed the series on 8 June 2012, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  16. ^ Charles Dale originally departed the series on 11 June 2016, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  17. ^ Clive Mantle originally departed the series on 28 February 1998, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  18. ^ Suzanne Packer originally departed the series on 22 August 2015, and made a cameo appearance on 27 August 2016.
  19. ^ Bleasdale originally departed the series on 3 November 2007, but has returned for guest appearances between 27 August 2016 and 30 September 2017.
  20. ^ Sunetra Sarker originally departed on 7 May 2016, but returned for one episode on 13 January 2018.
  21. ^ Sam Nicholls originally departed the series on 14 December 2013, before returning on 23 September 2017.
  22. ^ Quarshie appeared in two Casualty and Holby City crossover episodes and guest appeared in Casualty for two episodes in 2017.
  23. ^ a b Jhakra, St. Clement and Lawrence have previously made guest appearances.
  24. ^ Tom Chambers originally appeared in three episodes between 23 February and 9 September 2016, before returning on 11 February 2017. He departed on 22 July 2017.
